	<div style="text-align:right;">
		STRIEDER, Anna Paola<sup>1</sup>; JOHANN, Aline Cristina Batista<sup>2</sup>; VEIGA, Flavia Fusco<sup>3</sup>; GREGIO, Ana Maria Trindade<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
